data.title: Larry Johnson may have already provided the perfect answer to those questioning his Ohio State future: State of the Program
data.meta_description: Description Evaluating Ohio State football's defensive line room heading into a pivotal 2024 season.
data.text:
COLUMBUS, Ohio -- Ohio State is entering a pivotal moment in the tenure of Ryan Day as he enters his sixth year as head coach.

With this season comes a line in the sand for Day. The college football landscape has changed with an expanding College Football Playoff and expanding conference creating new variables to overcome for a man trying to right the ship against Michigan, regain Big Ten supremacy, and finally deliver a national title.
